short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Notifies the user when on the LinkedIn Saved Posts page and allows data extraction.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes use of your saved LinkedIn posts. This extension navigates to your posts, scrolls through all saved posts, and allows you to save as json or csv format.
